        Reads a set of JSON items from the JSON stream.

        An item is a complete value, which can be a JsonToken.START_OBJECT, or a value token.

        Parameters:
        parentInstance - the object the data is parsed into
        requiresJsonKey - when true indicates that the item will have a JSON key
        context - the JSON/YAML parsing context
        Returns:
        the items read, or null if no item was read
        Throws:
        IOException - if an error occurred reading the underlying XML file
